{"tid":1776393,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"前線手足短訊：128咁和平冇得打架，我地就嚟輸","createTime":"2019-12-09T13:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T15:23:33.000Z","uid":173921,"like":14,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fa018ceabbd6cf4e30fbbc8eef37b44e18f7cc","tid":1776393,"uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:33:46.000Z","msg":"前線手足短訊：和平行行企企嘅攻略我真係唔識，以前次次一行就開波打架嘛點會好似琴日咁和平，128竟然冇人掟磚掟火魔，冇人食二噁英放題，就嚟輸喇w<br />\n<br />\n正評：冇架打，就嚟輸<br />\n負評：不完美可接受要改善"},{"pid":"68e2a1b7760834a0a8f2846389f922761a315b9d","tid":1776393,"uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:33:58.000Z","msg":"自推（1/10）"},{"pid":"07b003b0eb3e6d67a4531c896741764ab6bb5e7f","tid":1776393,"uid":127553,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日遊行最深刻的一句「初夏&mdash;&mdash;寒冬」<br />\n我們不經不覺由初夏走到冬天<br />\n由撐黃色食店走到黃色經濟圈<br />\n香港人就是有心有力也有財力<br />\n<br />\n講返正題，以往每年聖誕聯歡/Re-U都總係會叫啲最方便快捷嘅KFC、PizzaHut聖誕套餐，今年相信大家都不了不了，所以我地整合左所有會做到會服務嘅黃店，大家識Do啦！<br />\n*（亦建議學生會將圖印出派比同學宣傳📃）<br />\n<br />\n最後，教育同行全體祝大家有個Yellow Christmas 🎄💛<br />\n<br />\n*我地已盡量向店方直接確認到會服務，但始終人手有限，資料未必齊全，歡迎各位Comment報料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=0101fdd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\nFb: shorturl.at/kqtJM<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstandbyeducatorshk%3Figshid%3Djuzv8s7rtxb5&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=fafa200c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5</a>"},{"p